data.description: Luxury awaits in this absolutely stunning condominium! This 6th floor, corner unit condo features gorgeous LVP floors that lead you to a modern kitchen, allowing you to prep your meals on shining quartz countertops with the help of stainless steel appliances. Then step into the spacious living room to enjoy an abundance of natural light pouring in from the windows and corner balcony. The owner's bedroom boasts plentiful space to relax in at the end of the day, with a generously sized walk-in closet and granite double vanity countertops in the en-suite bath that ensures elegance at every turn. The secondary bedroom has private access to the guest bathroom, allowing you and your guests to all enjoy your own privacy. The amenities further encompass the grandeur of the unit; this 24-hour guard gated community ensures immaculate property upkeep, secured same-level parking with 2 parking spots next to the entrance on your floor, concierge services, a clubroom with catering kitchen, and more, including social events! Adventure then continues outside the community, as One River Place is in the PRIME location of Atlanta.
